# Local-only diagnostic/build tools under cmd/. None are deployed: the Docker
# image builds only /app/server (Dockerfile line 20, `go build -o /build/server .`),
# so every cmd/ is a local Mac tool run against prod Mongo / SSH. All were
# removed from git tracking on 2026-06-27 (the bulk-fill tooling purge) and are
# kept here without polluting commits or the alt flatten.
cmd/
# Stray compiled binaries of cmd/ tools at repo root (root-anchored so they do
# not match the gitignored cmd/ source dirs).
/hingest
/tpbingest
/watchporningest
/yesporningest
